{"data":{"page":{"id":"74480dd5-548c-5bf3-8edb-119aa8c758cf","html":"<p class=\"work-links\">\n<a class=\"btn icon icon-external\" href=\"http://work.joanmira.com/webs/robertosilvosa/\" target=\"_blank\">Launch archived template</a></p>\n<p>Roberto Silvosa contacted me to design and build a custom website for his business with an special emphasis on the aesthetics. He also needed to be able to upload new photos of his floral projects.</p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 101%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/87c0f4798ee5faedebe84fdaaaab0f8c/6b333/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/87c0f4798ee5faedebe84fdaaaab0f8c/f3ce7/1.jpg 200w,\n/static/87c0f4798ee5faedebe84fdaaaab0f8c/72342/1.jpg 400w,\n/static/87c0f4798ee5faedebe84fdaaaab0f8c/6b333/1.jpg 800w,\n/static/87c0f4798ee5faedebe84fdaaaab0f8c/40247/1.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<p>The portfolio of works uses a book metaphor to swipe the photos, which are loaded from the custom CMS built for the Flash website. It also has a small product catalog and checkout system to allow customers to order products via email. The products in the catalog and the news are also controlled via CMS.</p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 63.3%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"2\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/4d6fa58b0cbf1d9615c75492fdd53ddf/6b333/2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4d6fa58b0cbf1d9615c75492fdd53ddf/f3ce7/2.jpg 200w,\n/static/4d6fa58b0cbf1d9615c75492fdd53ddf/72342/2.jpg 400w,\n/static/4d6fa58b0cbf1d9615c75492fdd53ddf/6b333/2.jpg 800w,\n/static/4d6fa58b0cbf1d9615c75492fdd53ddf/40247/2.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 65.20771513353115%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"3\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/45b18446e7e0c9d566169520765ab4cb/6b333/3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/45b18446e7e0c9d566169520765ab4cb/f3ce7/3.jpg 200w,\n/static/45b18446e7e0c9d566169520765ab4cb/72342/3.jpg 400w,\n/static/45b18446e7e0c9d566169520765ab4cb/6b333/3.jpg 800w,\n/static/45b18446e7e0c9d566169520765ab4cb/b2533/3.jpg 1200w,\n/static/45b18446e7e0c9d566169520765ab4cb/7cce5/3.